data.comment: The match is underway in Suita.
Ball goes out of play for a Yokohama FC goal kick.
In the minute 1, Throw-in for Gamba in the half of Yokohama FC.
Free kick Gamba.
Gamba's Shinya Yajima gets his shot away but it misses the target.
In the minute 4, Yokohama FC have a goal kick.
Ball safe as Yokohama FC is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Can Yokohama FC get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Gamba's half?
In the minute 5, Yukiei Hut signals a Yokohama FC throw-in in Gamba's half.
Yukiei Hut awards the home team a throw-in.
Yokohama FC needs to be cautious. Gamba have an attacking throw-in.
In the minute 7, Gamba's Yosuke Ideguchi misses with an attempt on goal.
Goal kick for Yokohama FC at Panasonic Stadium Suita.
A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
In the minute 9, It's a goal kick for the away team in Suita.
Yukiei Hut signals a throw-in for Yokohama FC, close to Gamba's area.
Yukiei Hut awards Gamba a goal kick.
In the minute 12, Gamba awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Free kick for Yokohama FC in their own half.
Yokohama FC's Koki Saito gets in a shot but it is blocked by a Gamba defender.
In the minute 14, Important block from the Gamba defence as Yusuke Minagawa fires in a strike for Yokohama FC.
Gamba are in shooting range from this free kick.
Gamba are pushing forward but Ademilson's finish is wide of the goal.
In the minute 17, Ball goes out of play for a Yokohama FC goal kick.
Gamba have been awarded a corner by Yukiei Hut.
In Suita, Gen Shoji of Gamba is presented with a shooting opportunity. But the strike is blocked by the covering defence.
In the minute 24, Yokohama FC to take a throw-in in Gamba territory.
Throw-in for Gamba in their own half.
Ademilson (Gamba) gets up for a header but cannot keep the ball on target.
In the minute 28, It's a goal kick for the away team in Suita.
Yokohama FC pushes forward through Takuya Matsuura, whose finish on goal is saved.
Yukiei Hut signals a free kick to Yokohama FC.
In the minute 34, Gamba take a 1-0 lead thanks to Ademilson.
Yuji Ono with an assist there.
Throw-in Gamba.
In the minute 36, Throw-in for Gamba at Panasonic Stadium Suita.
Yukiei Hut signals a free kick to Yokohama FC in their own half.
Free kick for Yokohama FC in the half of Gamba.
In the minute 38, Yukiei Hut awards the home team a throw-in.
Yokohama FC's Yusuke Minagawa is on target but unsuccessful.
Koki Saito for Yokohama FC drives towards goal at Panasonic Stadium Suita. But the finish is unsuccessful.
In the minute 44, Throw-in Gamba.
Gamba drives forward and Yuji Ono gets in a shot. Without netting, however.
Yukiei Hut will wait an extra 2 minutes before blowing the whistle to end the 1st half.
In the minute 45, Yokohama FC advance rapidly upfield but Yukiei Hut blows for offside.
In Suita, Gamba push forward quickly but are pulled up for offside.
The first-half is over at Panasonic Stadium Suita.
In the minute 46, The second-half has just kicked-off.
A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
Can Gamba get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Yokohama FC's half?
In the minute 47, In Suita a free kick has been awarded the home team.
Yokohama FC awarded a free kick in their own half.
Kosuke Onose (Gamba) has been booked and must now be careful not to get a second yellow card.
In the minute 51, Corner awarded to Yokohama FC.
Maguinho (Yokohama FC) gets in a powerful header but the ball is cleared away.
Koki Saito's header is off-target for Yokohama FC.
In the minute 53, Gamba have a goal kick.
In Suita a free kick has been awarded the home team.
Yokohama FC's Takuya Matsuura breaks free at Panasonic Stadium Suita. But the strike goes wide of the post.
In the minute 57, Yukiei Hut awards Gamba a goal kick.
Yokohama FC drive upfield and Yutaro Hakamata gets in a shot. The strike is blocked by a Gamba defender.
Koki Saito is on target to level the scores at 1-1.
In the minute 62, Gamba to take a throw-in in Yokohama FC territory.
Patric is replacing Ademilson for Gamba at Panasonic Stadium Suita.
Shu Kurata is on a sub for Yuji Ono for Gamba.
In the minute 63, Yokohama FC drive forward at breakneck speed but are pulled up for offside.
Throw-in for Yokohama FC at Panasonic Stadium Suita.
Yukiei Hut signals a Yokohama FC throw-in in Gamba's half.
In the minute 66, Yusuke Matsuo (Yokohama FC) strikes at Panasonic Stadium Suita but his header is cleared.
Yokohama FC awarded a free kick in their own half.
Yokohama FC are caught offside.
In the minute 70, Gamba have a dangerous throw-in.
Free kick in a good position for Yokohama FC!
Yokohama FC make their first substitution with Leandro Domingues replacing Koki Saito.
In the minute 74, Takahiro Shimotaira (Yokohama FC) is making a second substitution, with Yuki Kusano replacing Takuya Matsuura.
Leandro Domingues gets his shot on target but fails to score for Yokohama FC.
Throw-in for Gamba in the half of Yokohama FC.
In the minute 75, Yokohama FC awarded a throw-in in their own half.
In Suita Yokohama FC drive forward through Yuki Kusano. His shot is on target but it's saved.
Leandro Domingues of Yokohama FC gets in a strike, but is off target.
In the minute 77, Goal kick for Gamba at Panasonic Stadium Suita.
Gamba are whistled for offside.
Ryu Takao is replacing Kosuke Onose for the home team.
In the minute 79, The home team have replaced Hiroki Fujiharu with Yuya Fukuda. This is the fourth substitution made today by Tsuneyasu Miyamoto.
Ball safe as Gamba is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Yukiei Hut signals a free kick to Yokohama FC in their own half.
In the minute 81, Kim Young-Gwon is booked for the home team.
Free kick Gamba.
Takahiro Shimotaira is making the team's third substitution at Panasonic Stadium Suita with Kohei Tezuka replacing Maguinho.
In the minute 83, Patric for the home team is judged to be offside.
Throw-in for Yokohama FC in their own half.
Ball safe as Yokohama FC is awarded a throw-in in their half.
In the minute 85, Tsuneyasu Miyamoto (Gamba) is making a fifth substitution, with Kazuma Watanabe replacing Takashi Usami.
Yusuke Minagawa for Yokohama FC gets in a strike but fails to hit the target.
Goal kick for Gamba at Panasonic Stadium Suita.
In the minute 87, Yokohama FC's Leandro Domingues gets in a shot on goal at Panasonic Stadium Suita. But the effort is unsuccessful.
Yokohama FC have been awarded a corner by Yukiei Hut.
In the minute 88, Free kick for Gamba in their own half.
The away team replace Yusuke Minagawa with Ibba.
Ball goes out of play for a Yokohama FC goal kick.
Throw-in for Yokohama FC in the half of Gamba.
At Panasonic Stadium Suita the fourth official shows that 4 minutes will be added to the 2nd half.
Yokohama FC to take a throw-in in Gamba territory.
Gamba awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Yuya Fukuda (Gamba) gets in a strike but the shot is blocked by a defender.
Shinya Yajima (Gamba) goes for goal but the shot is blocked by an alert defence.
Yosuke Ideguchi (Gamba) is given an opening but the shot is blocked by a defender.
Corner awarded to Gamba.
Can Gamba capitalize from this throw-in deep inside Yokohama FC's half?
Gamba have been awarded a corner by Yukiei Hut.
Yukiei Hut blows to end the match. The final score is 2-1.
Goal! A Patric header gives Gamba a 2-1 lead in Suita.
Great play from Yosuke Ideguchi to set up the goal.
